media:group.media:title: From Horrible to Deplorable - Leafyishere's Story (Calvin Lee Vail)
media:group.media:description:
Leafyishere has been through many ordeals in and outside YouTube, but it was clear that any thing he put enough effort in saw success. From running a Minecraft server to running a channel that netted him millions of dollars Leafy did it all, he just did it too well and loud. In the process of growing his channel he brought down other channels symbolically getting enough attention through it to get his own channel taken down literally.
